{"tid":2478764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【11.11 旺角】被控管鐳射筆伸縮棍　青年無律師代表　將親自盤問證人","createTime":"2021-04-07T09:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T11:43:44.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"280bbbee176ec23c3a0969955c015d2289162ea5","tid":2478764,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:55:53.000Z","msg":"2019 年 11 月 11 日，有人號召「黎明行動」，呼籲市民「三罷」，各區發生衝突。兩青年被控在旺角管鐳射筆和伸縮棍，案件今（7 日）在西九龍裁判法院開審。其中一名 20 歲青年認罪，他早前因本案一度遭還押兩個半月，裁判官香淑嫻押後到 4 月 21 日判刑，以索取背景及社會服務令報告，期間准他保釋。另一名<span class=\"red\">18 歲青年則不認罪</span>，無律師代表，親自審訊和盤問證人。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指，被告當日受網絡影響，並無完善計劃，在現場見到三位年輕人便同行，行了一段短路後便被捕，涉案物品從未被使用，亦無人受傷或財物受損壞。<span class=\"red\">辯方強調次被告曾還押 2 個半月</span>，希望法庭考慮判處社會服務令。裁判官押後至 4 月 21 日判刑，以索取背景及社會服務令報告，<span class=\"red\">期間准被告保釋</span>。"},{"pid":"4ef098e3d5fbe65040c10140c0f417772473cb70","tid":2478764,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:56:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-11-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E7%AE%A1%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E4%BC%B8%E7%B8%AE%E6%A3%8D-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E7%84%A1%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8-%E5%B0%87%E8%A6%AA%E8%87%AA%E7%9B%A4%E5%95%8F%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-11-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E4%25BC%25B8%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E6%25A3%258D-%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%2595%258F%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtLXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=ea5613aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-11-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E4%25BC%25B8%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E6%25A3%258D-%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%2595%258F%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&h=c0279798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-11-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E7%AE%A1%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E4%BC%B8%E7%B8%AE%E6%A3%8D-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E7%84%A1%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8-%E5%B0%87%E8%A6%AA%E8%87%AA%E7%9B%A4%E5%95%8F%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%BA/</a>"},{"pid":"8dc87df06749fb1a6d8aa107d8672a60c5dbe956","tid":2478764,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c23af17010af55bb69b295656193882791dd7ef","tid":2478764,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"被告向法庭陳述案情時則指，當時<span class=\"red\">王從他身上或背包搜出的物品中，均無包括雷射筆</span>。而當王完成搜查並將物品從地上放回背包時，則「somehow （以某種未知原因）」將一支雷射筆一併放入，然後將他帶回警署。後來王在警署內把被告背包及內裡物品放進透明證物袋時，<span class=\"red\">被告才首次發現雷射筆的存在</span>。<br />\n<br />\n王否認，堅稱：「我喺佢（被告）視線範圍內做，亦都有叫佢望住。」<br />\n<br />\n被告再向法庭指出案情，認為王曾在警車上把萬用鉗從鎖匙串解除，質疑王干預證物。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/RNTPC3PJ2FCKHAHEUD7DREGSV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FRNTPC3PJ2FCKHAHEUD7DREGSV4%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtLXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=f7ff220a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FRNTPC3PJ2FCKHAHEUD7DREGSV4%2F&h=263de371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/RNTPC3PJ2FCKHAHEUD7DREGSV4/</a>"},{"pid":"36b02e104db8334df1cc3d555c6cc4bc07914473","tid":2478764,"uid":110043